{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778991907668,"sessionID":"ses_1cbe431a9ffeF6wJ2aoUeVp53Q","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"apply_patch","callID":"call_vJyQCsRuo7Ie5IhijtIGfTO5","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"patchText":"*** Begin Patch\n*** Add File: /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n+Addressed in PR #<NN>.\n+\n+Summary:\n+- corrected a set of oxidoreductase molecular function term parentages to align with the cited EC subclasses\n+- updated several labels and reaction definitions to match the current RHEA/EC representation\n+- added `term_tracker_item` links back to issue `#31969` on the affected terms\n+- validated the ontology successfully with `make travis_build`\n+\n+The largest changes were in the `1.14`, `1.17`, and related oxidoreductase sub-branches, including fixes for misplaced monooxygenase/dioxygenase and CH/CH2 donor terms.\n*** Add File: /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENTS.md\n+This PR addresses issue `#31969` by correcting a batch of misparented oxidoreductase activity terms in the molecular function branch and updating several term labels/definitions to match the cited EC and RHEA chemistry.\n+\n+Main changes:\n+- Renamed `GO:0102394` from `4-hydroxy-L-isoleucine dehydrogenase activity` to `L-isoleucine 4-hydroxylase activity` and reparented it under `GO:0016706`.\n+- Renamed `GO:0050607` to `S-(hydroxymethyl)mycothiol dehydrogenase activity`, updated its reaction definition to the RHEA reaction, and moved it from the aldehyde/oxo NAD(P) parent to `GO:0016616`.\n+- Reparented EC `1.17` formate/CH or CH2 donor terms (`GO:0008863`, `GO:0047899`, `GO:0047111`, `GO:0008839`) from inappropriate `1.2`/`1.3` parents to `GO:0016726` or `GO:0016725` as appropriate.\n+- Reparented several oxygenase terms to the correct EC-aligned parents:\n+  - `GO:0010277` to `GO:0016709`\n+  - `GO:0050588` to `GO:0016702`\n+  - `GO:0018570` to `GO:0016708`\n+  - `GO:0004498` and `GO:0036199` to `GO:0016713`\n+  - `GO:0050616` and `GO:0102915` to `GO:0016717`\n+  - `GO:0033759`, `GO:0045431`, `GO:0047594`, and `GO:0050589` to `GO:0050498`\n+  - `GO:0102717` back to `GO:0016706`\n+- Reparented additional oxidoreductase terms with mismatched EC subclass placement:\n+  - `GO:0008762` to `GO:0016628`\n+  - `GO:0018525` to `GO:0016614`\n+  - `GO:0044684` to `GO:0016645`\n+  - `GO:0033717` to `GO:0016614`\n+  - `GO:0106145` to `GO:0016706`\n+- Updated term definitions where requested to match RHEA-style reaction text for:\n+  - `GO:0008762`\n+  - `GO:0018525`\n+  - `GO:0044684`\n+  - `GO:0047081`\n+  - `GO:0106145`\n+  - `GO:0102717`\n+  - `GO:0050616`\n+  - `GO:0102915`\n+  - `GO:0032441`\n+- Added `property_value: term_tracker_item \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31969\" xsd:anyURI` to the affected edited terms.\n+\n+Validation:\n+- Pre-validation: `make travis_build` passed before edits.\n+- Post-edit validation: `make travis_build` passed after edits.\n+\n+Research and design-pattern notes:\n+- RESEARCH: N/A for this issue. The issue already supplied a concrete, term-by-term set of EC/RHEA-backed corrections, and the edits were constrained to parentage, labels, and reaction definitions.\n+- DESIGN-PATTERNS: reviewed existing oxidoreductase parent structure and similar catalytic activity terms; no new logical definitions or `intersection_of` axioms were introduced.\n+\n+Checklist:\n+- [x] PLAN: analyzed issue context and mapped requested term-by-term changes\n+- [x] PRE-VALIDATION: current ontology validated before edits\n+- [x] RESEARCH: N/A\n+- [x] TERM-SEARCH: inspected all affected terms and target parent terms in `go-edit.obo`\n+- [x] DESIGN-PATTERNS: reviewed existing catalytic activity structure; no new logical defs added\n+- [x] EDITS: used checkout/checkin workflow via `terms/`\n+- [x] RELATIONSHIPS: updated asserted parents only where EC placement was incorrect\n+- [x] SPECIALIZED-EDITS: used `/reaction` guidance for catalytic activity term handling\n+- [x] ME